{"tid":1236650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人記住唔好收貨呀","createTime":"2019-06-17T13:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T13:16:27.000Z","uid":89353,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"21c54b1e560e778ea755655b88fbc02af21e7f35","tid":1236650,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:03:24.000Z","msg":"一日未下台一日未普選<br />\n就算唔定為暴動<br />\n徹回惡法<br />\n都唔好中計<br />\n我地冇贏<br />\n只係一直輸緊 <br />\n啱啱先開始反擊翻小小咋<br />\n我地仲輸緊<br />\n仲有23條 國歌法 南大嶼<br />\n我地唔可以停<br />\n甚至未講我地既立法會有功能組別依個制度上問題<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得我地應該妥協 至少都要等到佢地下台<br />\n千其唔好中佢哋計"},{"pid":"187fb55d45cfe64667b37508dd1fd06226105883","tid":1236650,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:06:24.000Z","msg":"唔該幫手一齊周圍post：<br />\n反送中Deadline、黑警、醫管局、所有被捕政治犯、撤回暴動定性。<br />\n不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰、不譴責。加油！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6aa047a51cccdfd8e4817e8ba5a0428d0aa10f","tid":1236650,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"187fb55d45cfe64667b37508dd1fd06226105883","tid":1236650,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:06:24.000Z","msg":"唔該幫手一齊周圍post：<br />\n反送中Deadline、黑警、醫管局、所有被捕政治犯、撤回暴動定性。<br />\n不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰、不譴責。加油！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgm